The Core Infrastructure Initiative also invested 120,000 USD for education to the good practices of open-source development, 120,000 USD in popular open-source project analysis and 95,000 USD for auditing OpenSSL<ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.coreinfrastructure.org/sites/cii/files/cii_annualreport_2016_fnl_digital.pdf/ | title=Core Infrastructure Initiative 2016 Annual Report | publisher=The Core Infrastructure Initiative | accessdate=14 April 2017}}</ref>

